data.title: andy-roberts.net
data.meta_description: Personal website of Andrew Roberts, a senior software engineer based in the UK.
data.text:
I'm a co-founder of Jellybooks, an online digital service that is a leader in reader analytics and web-based ebook technology. We provide myriad services to help publishers to understand and serve their target audiences.

The vast majority of visitors on this site are looking for LaTeX typesetting help. My LaTeX tutorials have served beginners all over the globe for almost two decades and proved more popular than I ever expected.
